* Dinobot watched Tavatron begin to run and shook his head, a smile 
threatening. Did she never give up?!
He looked quickly back down the bank then sprang into action and began to 
follow Tavatron at a fast pace, he soon came up behind her at a dead run.
Dinobot realized how fast he was going and thought if he was to stop quick 
he would most likely land on his snout, hard!
How could a wolf go so fast?*

" Where are you taking us?"

* He was curious as to what terrain Tavatron planned to practice upon, it 
was always wise to get an idea for future advantages.*
